https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&mid=2247558316&idx=1&sn=6a53c77fe9bdb8b35a1d513897c4a472","date":"2026-02-09 00:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_bdde6ae5.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"阿里云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":37,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_10810d0b","title":"2026-02-11 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-11-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-11 08:05:26","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_10810d0b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":67,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_9aa6b0d9","title":"[AINews] Qwen Image 2 与 Seedance 2","link":"https://www.latent.space/p/ainews-qwen-image-2-and-seedance","date":"2026-02-11 05:19:52","oneSentenceSummary":"本技术摘要涵盖了 Qwen-Image 2.0 和 Seedance 2.0 的发布，以及 AI 编程智能体、MoE 训练优化和 AI 驱动药物研发方面的重大更新。","summary":"本文提供了 2026 年 2 月 9 日至 10 日 AI 领域的密集摘要。重点包括阿里巴巴的 Qwen-Image 2.0，这是一个统一了图像生成与编辑、支持 2K 分辨率的 7B 模型；以及字节跳动的 Seedance 2.0，该模型在视频物理特性和运动方面表现出显著改进。文章详细介绍了 OpenAI Responses API 的演进，以支持长时间运行的智能体任务和托管沙箱。此外还介绍了技术突破，如 Unsloth 的 Triton 内核实现了 12 倍的 MoE 训练加速，以及关于 GLM-5 和 Qwen 3.5 的架构泄露。报告还涵盖了 Isomorphic Labs 的 IsoDDE，据称其在生物分子结构预测方面的性能是 AlphaFold 3 的两倍。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_9aa6b0d9.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Latent Space","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":23,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_bdb65f4d","title":"英伟达两篇论文，带来了 VLA 之后具身智能的新范式｜Hao 好聊趋势","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjc1NjM3MjY2MA==&mid=2691564747&idx=1&sn=323c91eb1d9984890df2e56239646810","date":"2026-02-11 04:42:00","oneSentenceSummary":"英伟达通过 DreamZero 和 DreamDojo 两篇论文，提出从 VLA 转向基于视频生成的世界动作模型（WAM），实现了具身智能在物理理解、零样本泛化及跨机体学习上的重大突破。","summary":"本文深度解析了英伟达在具身智能领域的最新研究成果。针对传统 VLA（视觉-语言-动作）模型缺乏物理常识、泛化能力弱且极度依赖昂贵遥操作数据的痛点，英伟达推出了 DreamZero 和 DreamDojo 两大框架。DreamZero 通过自回归 Diffusion Transformer (DiT) 架构同步预测视频与动作，并利用 Flash 技术解决生成速度瓶颈，实现了惊人的零样本泛化能力；DreamDojo 则通过“连续潜在动作”技术，解锁了海量互联网视频资源，使机器人能通过观看人类视频学习物理规律。这一转变标志着具身智能从“语义映射”进化到“物理模拟”的新范式。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_bdb65f4d.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"腾讯科技","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":30,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_9d37a854","title":"科学家与模拟器","link":"https://www.latent.space/p/scientist-simulator","date":"2026-02-10 15:27:58","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_9d37a854.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Latent Space","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":11,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_6beedfd2","title":"AI 硬件闭门探讨：未来硬件只是数据的入口，接下来是「软件定义硬件」的时代","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg5NTc0MjgwMw==&mid=2247522680&idx=1&sn=492c68738d2531bd653e7f84ec276781","date":"2026-02-10 11:29:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_6beedfd2.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Founder Park","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":26,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_15cd3e76","title":"面对  OpenClaw，苹果选择刀背藏身","link":"https://www.ifanr.com/1654588?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=","date":"2026-02-10 09:36:09","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_15cd3e76.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"爱范儿","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":16,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_48712280","title":"科技创新如何助力中华优秀传统文化传承发展？｜来自“腾讯探元计划 2024”的启示","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTE0ODA2MQ==&mid=2650995893&idx=1&sn=57452c0513b168e09f018aae2068100e","date":"2026-02-10 09:01:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文系统总结了腾讯“探元计划”通过“五步法”与“三级火箭”模式，利用 AI 等前沿技术破解文化遗产保护难题，构建可持续文化科技创新生态的实践经验。","summary":"文章深入探讨了科技创新在中华优秀传统文化传承中的关键作用，并以腾讯“探元计划 2024”为核心案例，详细阐述了文化科技融合的创新范式。文章提出了“聚焦真问题、探寻真解法、共创真方案、匹配真要素、放大真价值”的五步法，并构建了从高校实验室概念验证（0 到 1）、场景落地验证（1 到 10）到规模化推广（10 到 N）的“三级火箭”路径。同时，文章直面当前文化科技融合中存在的“人文缺位”、技术供需错配及跨界人才断层等挑战，通过甲骨文大模型、石窟虚拟修复等具体案例，展示了 AI 与文化遗产深度融合的潜力，最后展望了构建开放、协同、共益的文化科技创新生态的未来愿景。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_48712280.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"腾讯研究院","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":17,"score":83},{"id":"RAW_796ba472","title":"2026-02-10 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-10-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-10 09:00:56","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_796ba472.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":66,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_62b21a05","title":"[AINews] “带有一丝疯狂色彩的科幻”","link":"https://www.latent.space/p/ainews-sci-fi-with-a-touch-of-madness","date":"2026-02-10 04:33:06","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_62b21a05.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Latent Space","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":25,"score":84},{"id":"RAW_ae00ea60","title":"程前访谈陈森雁：我裁掉了 20 人的拍摄团队，一年白捡 100 万","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxNTAzNzU0Ng==&mid=2654903209&idx=2&sn=e4f0836c0a169cb7e61a4da47a576130","date":"2026-02-09 13:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ae00ea60.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"笔记侠","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":18,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_5585a96a","title":"即梦 Seedance2.0 视频模型\"王者归来\"之后 | 最新突发: 模型太强以至禁止了真人人脸支持...","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxODUzNTg2MA==&mid=2247489943&idx=1&sn=b77584f14c2c449d78b6c1e169cc67b1","date":"2026-02-09 10:29:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_5585a96a.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Web3天空之城","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":13,"score":82},{"id":"RAW_96a3c531","title":"2026-02-09 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-09-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-09 08:57:18","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_96a3c531.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":67,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_d27d64c0","title":"2026 年人工智能+的共识与分歧","link":"https://